  <lemma xml:id="lecture-notes-lem-how-to-multiply-complex-numbers">
    <title>How to Multiply Complex Numbers</title>
    <statement>
      <p>
        Let <m>a+bi</m> and <m>c+di</m> be any two complex numbers.
        Then
        <me>(a+bi)(c+di)=(ac-bd)+(ad+bc)i</me>.
      </p>
      <p>
        In other words, just FOIL it out and simplify using <m>i^2=-1</m>.
      </p>
    </statement>
  </lemma>

